from heapq import heappush, heappop
from collections import defaultdict

n = int(input())
s = [input() for i in range(n)]
start = tuple("sssssssssss")
goal = tuple("ggggggggggg")
s.append("ggggggggggg;")
v = defaultdict(list)
la = tuple([start[i] for i in range(11)])
k = 0
for i in s:
    if i[:4] == "goto":
        v[la].append((tuple(i[5:-1]),k))
        k += 1
    else:
        v[la].append((tuple(i[:-1]),k))
        la = tuple([i[j] for j in range(len(i)-1)])
        k = 0
q = [(0,start)]
dist = defaultdict(lambda : float("inf"))
dist[start] = 0
while q:
    dx,x = heappop(q)
    for y,d in v[x]:
        if dx + d < dist[y]:
            dist[y] = dx+d
            heappush(q,(dist[y],y))
print(dist[goal])

while True:
    n=int(input())
    if n==0:
        break
    books=[]
    read_t=0
    write_t=0
    for i in range(n):
        r,w=map(int,input().split())
        read_t+=r
        write_t+=w
        books.append((r,w))
    books=sorted(books)
    if books[-1][0]<=read_t//2:
        print(read_t+write_t)
        continue
    sukima=books[-1][0]-(read_t-books[-1][0])
    dp=[[0 for i in range(sukima+1)] for i in range(n)]
    for i in range(1,n):
        for j in range(1,sukima+1):
            dp[i][j]=max(dp[i-1][j],
            dp[i-1][j-books[i-1][1]]
            +books[i-1][1] if j-books[i-1][1]>=0 else 0)

    print(read_t+write_t+sukima-dp[-1][-1])
